ture content of the subfloor should be within +/- 2% of the moisture content of the new floor to be laid.\n\nAttained moisture content of wood flooring exposed to variations in temperature and humidity.\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"21\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">Relative Humidity (%)</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td class=\"top\">5</td>\n<td class=\"top\">10</td>\n<td class=\"top\">15</td>\n<td class=\"top\">20</td>\n<td class=\"top\">25</td>\n<td class=\"top\">30</td>\n<td class=\"top\">35</td>\n<td class=\"top\">40</td>\n<td class=\"top\">45</td>\n<td class=\"top\">50</td>\n<td class=\"top\">55</td>\n<td class=\"top\">60</td>\n<td class=\"top\">65</td>\n<td class=\"top\">70</td>\n<td class=\"top\">75</td>\n<td class=\"top\">80</td>\n<td class=\"top\">85</td>\n<td class=\"top\">90</td>\n<td class=\"top\">95</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td class=\"top\">30</td>\n<td>1.4</td>\n<td>2.6</td>\n<td>3.7</td>\n<td>4.6</td>\n<td>5.5</td>\n<td>6.3</td>\n<td>7.1</td>\n<td>7.9</td>\n<td>8.7</td>\n<td>9.5</td>\n<td>10.4</td>\n<td>11.3</td>\n<td>12.4</td>\n<td>13.5</td>\n<td>14.9</td>\n<td>16.5</td>\n<td>18.5</td>\n<td>21.0</td>\n<td>24.3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td class=\"top\">40</td>\n<td>1.4</td>\n<td>2.6</td>\n<td>3.7</td>\n<td>4.6</td>\n<td>5.5</td>\n<td>6.3</td>\n<td>7.1</td>\n<td>7.9</td>\n<td>8.7</td>\n<td>9.5</td>\n<td>10.4</td>\n<td>11.3</td>\n<td>12.3</td>\n<td>13.5</td>\n<td>14.9</td>\n<td>16.5</td>\n<td>18.5</td>\n<td>21.0</td>\n<td>24.3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td class=\"top\">50</td>\n<td>1.4</td>\n<td>2.6</td>\n<td>3.6</td>\n<td>4.6</td>\n<td>5.5</td>\n<td>6.3</td>\n<td>7.1</td>\n<td>7.9</td>\n<td>8.7</td>\n<td>9.5</td>\n<td>10.3</td>\n<td>11.2</td>\n<td>12.3</td>\n<td>13.4</td>\n<td>14.8</td>\n<td>16.4</td>\n<td>18.4</td>\n<td>20.9</td>\n<td>24.3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Temperature (°F)</td>\n<td class=\"top\">60</td>\n<td>1.3</td>\n<td>2.5</td>\n<td>3.6</td>\