flooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-524\" title=\"wentworth 370x243\" src=\"http://www.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243-300x197.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"197\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-523\" title=\"unfin wal 370x243\" src=\"http://www.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243-300x197.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"197\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFixing methods offered depend on individual site situations &amp; conditions and and also on client\'s or architect\'s stipulations. The methods include:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully glued down onto solid screed</li>\r\n	<li>Floated over solid screed/ joists/ plywood / chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Secret nailed to joists / plywood</li>\r\n	<li>Secret screwed to chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Face fixed and plugged to joists / plywood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen considering a new Oak floor or Walnut flooring, always be aware that the complex task of installing a wood floor, whether solid wood or engineered wood flooring, is best left to an expert wood floor installer. A trained and experienced wood floor fitter will have the wherewithal to assess site conditions, measure and record moisture / humidity levels, assess the suitability of the subfloor, address any likely issues, suggest the most appropriate fixing method and materials to be used and be able to install the floor to the client\'s complete satisfaction. Such a fitter will also be able to advise with regard to the care and maintenance of your wooden floor. Be aware that a dedicated carpet fitter or laminate fitter might well not have the required training or experience required.','Wood Floor Fitting Service','','publish','open','open','','fitting-hardwood-flooring','','','2012-01-20 09:43:01','2012-01-20 09:43:01','',0,'http://dev.justwoodflo