ed but unfinished oak and walnut flooring is then machine sanded and also wire brushed if required. The floor boards are then further processed through state of the art finishing plant, to a variety of beautifully attractive finishes (having been brushed/distressed/fumed/limed or hand scraped as required).\r\n\r\nJust Wood Flooring\'s stock finishes available include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lacquered</li>\r\n	<li>UV Cured Oiled</li>\r\n	<li>Brushed &amp; Oiled</li>\r\n	<li>Smoked, Brushed &amp; Oiled</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAlternatively, a \"tailor made\" finishing service is offered, by Just Wood Flooring, to cater for special bespoke wooden flooring requirements including aged patina, hand distressing, liming and hand scraping enhancements. Please contact Just Wood Flooring to discuss your exact finishing requirements.\r\n\r\n</div>','Solid Hardwood Flooring','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-19','','','2011-07-10 15:24:52','2011-07-10 15:24:52','',6,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/6-revision-19/',0,'revision','',0),(604,1,'2011-10-08 19:28:12','2011-10-08 19:28:12','<h2><a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/DSC02451a.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-280\" title=\"DSC02451a\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/DSC02451a-300x271.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"271\" /></a>Add a Bespoke Factory Finish to Your Hardwood Floor.</h2>\r\nIn addition to our extensive range of Oak floor boards, available from stock, Just Wood Flooring is pleased to offer a bespoke finishing service, applicable to our unfinished wood flooring (both solid and engineered).\r\n\r\nThis \"tailor made\" finishing service is particularly useful where discerning clients have very specific needs, such as where attempting to match to existing Oak floor boards or perhaps to an Oak staircase, furniture or joinery.\r\nAvailable Finishing Options.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li> Lacquering – various levels of sheen</li>\r\n	<li> Tinting –