partment. Walnut floors look good either lacquered, oiled or waxed but we would advise that the latter two options are by far the most practical. The lacquered variety can scratch fairly easily and as with many other dark hardwoods the scratches show light coloured and thus stand out. Oils and waxes are much more forgiving in this respect, as light scratches will virtually disappear with the wipe of an oil or wax bearing cloth. Deeper scratches can be sanded and re-oiled or re-waxed.','Engineered Walnut 15/18mm ','','inherit','open','open','','466-revision-10','','','2011-10-13 16:00:08','2011-10-13 16:00:08','',466,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/466-revision-10/',0,'revision','',0),(544,1,'2011-10-13 16:00:44','2011-10-13 16:00:44','American Black Walnut engineered floorboards are manufactured from one of the most highly prized hardwood species the world over. Walnut flooring has a beautifully decorative fine grain, displaying striking colours and grain texture. Walnut flooring is equally at home in a listed period property or in a modern city living apartment. Walnut floors look good either lacquered, oiled or waxed but we would advise that the latter two options are by far the most practical. The lacquered variety can scratch fairly easily and as with many other dark hardwoods the scratches show light coloured and thus stand out. Oils and waxes are much more forgiving in this respect, as light scratches will virtually disappear with the wipe of an oil or wax bearing cloth. Deeper scratches can be sanded and re-oiled or re-waxed.','Engineered Walnut 15/18mm ','','inherit','open','open','','466-revision-11','','','2011-10-13 16:00:44','2011-10-13 16:00:44','',466,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/466-revision-11/',0,'revision','',0),(545,1,'2011-10-03 18:16:24','2011-10-03 18:16:24','The term Oak parquet flooring simply refers to a mosaic arrangement or pattern of solid Oak blocks. It is a traditional method of floor covering dating back to the 17th century. Usually laid over solid screed floors and fully glued down using an appropriate wood floor adhesive. It is, however,  also suited to installation onto plywood [of minimum 18mm thickness] run over joists. The blocks sometimes tongued and grooved but often square edged are glued directly to the sub-floor but not to one another. The floor is then sanded flat and finally oiled or lacquered.','Solid Oak Parquet Flooring','','inherit','open','open','','352-revision-17','','','2011-10-03 18:16:24','2011-10-03 18:16:24','',352,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/352-revision-17/',0,'revision','',0),(546,1,'2011-10-13 16:22:43','2011-10-13 16:22:43','The term Oak parquet flooring simply refers to a mosaic arrangement or pattern of solid Oak blocks. It is a traditional method of floor covering dating back to the 17th century. Usually laid over solid screed floors and fully glued down using an appropriate wood floor adhesive. It is, however,  also suited to installation onto plywood [of minimum 18mm thickness] run over joists. The blocks sometimes tongued and grooved but often square edged are glued directly to the sub-floor but not to one another. Once installed, the Oak parquet flooring blocks are then sanded flat and finally finished with a number of coats of flooring oil, hard waxoil or lacquer.\r\n\r\nSolid Oak parquet flooring, available from our  York warehouse, provides a considerable advantage in terms of installation time. The individual blocks are loosely held together with a thin web or mesh backing. The blocks can thus be laid rapidly in sets of 15 to 72 individual blocks at a time. These lay directly onto the notch trowel applied flooring adhesive.','Solid Oak Parquet Flooring','','inherit','open','open','','352-revision-18','','','2011-10-13 16:22:43','2011-10-13 16:22:43','',352,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/352-revision-18/',0,'revision','',0),(547,1,'2011-10-13 16:36:34','2011-10-13 16:36:34','The term Oak parquet flooring simply refers to a mosaic arrangement or pattern of solid Oak blocks. It is a traditional method of floor covering dating back to the 17th century. Usually laid over solid screed floors and fully glued down using an appropriate wood floor adhesive. It is, however,  also suited to installation onto plywood [of minimum 18mm thickness] run over joists. The blocks sometimes tongued and grooved but often square edged are glued directly to the sub-floor but not to one another. Once installed, the Oak parquet flooring blocks are then sanded flat and finally finished with a number of coats of flooring oil, hard waxoil or lacquer.\r\n\r\nSolid Oak parquet flooring, available from our York warehouse, provides a considerable advantage in terms of installation time. The individual blocks are loosely held together with a thin web or mesh backing. The blocks can thus be laid rapidly in sets of 15 to 72 individual blocks at a time. These lay directly onto the notch trowel applied flooring adhesive.\r\n\r\nOak parquet blocks provide a particularly practical wood floor option in that damaged blocks can be easily repaired or replaced. Loose blocks can relatively easily be re-set. Used parquet blocks are indeed often reclaimed and sold in reclamation yards. These can be cleaned and re-laid, albeit at the expense of many hours of labour and exertion. New blocks particularly those meshed in sets offer a far more cost effective solution in terms of installation sums.','Solid Oak Parquet Flooring','','inherit','open','open','','352-revision-19','','','2011-10-13 16:36:34','2011-10-13 16:36:34','',352,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/352-revision-19/',0,'revision','',0),(548,1,'2011-10-11 20:47:06','2011-10-11 20:47:06','<a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-524\" title=\"wentworth 370x243\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"243\" /></a> <a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-523\" title=\"unfin wal 370x243\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"243\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe professional wood floor fitters employed by Justwood Flooring are experienced in all methods of wood floor installation.\r\n\r\nFixing methods offered depend on individual site situations &amp; conditions and and also on client\'s or architect\'s stipulations. The methods include:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully glued down onto solid screed</li>\r\n	<li>Floated over solid screed/ joists/ plywood / chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Secret nailed to joists / plywood</li>\r\n	<li>Secret screwed to chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Face fixed and plugged to joists / plywood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;','Wood Floor Fitting Service','','inherit','open','open','','167-revision-12','','','2011-10-11 20:47:06','2011-10-11 20:47:06','',167,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/167-revision-12/',0,'revision','',0),(549,1,'2011-10-14 14:23:29','2011-10-14 14:23:29','<a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-524\" title=\"wentworth 370x243\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"243\" /></a> <a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-523\" title=\"unfin wal 370x243\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"243\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe professional wood floor fitters employed by Justwood Flooring are experienced in all methods of wood floor installation.\r\n\r\nFixing methods offered depend on individual site situations &amp; conditions and and also on client\'s or architect\'s stipulations. The methods include:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully glued down onto solid screed</li>\r\n	<li>Floated over solid screed/ joists/ plywood / chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Secret nailed to joists / plywood</li>\r\n	<li>Secret screwed to chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Face fixed and plugged to joists / plywood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\ngsbsgbs','Wood Floor Fitting Service','','inherit','open','open','','167-revision-13','','','2011-10-14 14:23:29','2011-10-14 14:23:29','',167,'http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/167-revision-13/',0,'revision','',0),(550,1,'2011-10-14 14:36:44','2011-10-14 14:36:44','<a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-524\" title=\"wentworth 370x243\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/wentworth-370x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"243\" /></a> <a href=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-523\" title=\"unfin wal 370x243\" src=\"http://dev.justwoodflooring.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfin-wal-370x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"243\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe professional wood floor fitters employed by Justwood Flooring are experienced in all methods of wood floor installation.\r\n\r\nFixing methods offered depend on individual site situations &amp; conditions and and also on client\'s or architect\'s stipulations. The methods include:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully glued down onto solid screed</li>\r\n	<li>Floated over solid screed/ joists/ plywood / chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Secret nailed to joists / plywood</li>\r\n	<li>Secret screwed to chipboard</li>\r\n	<li>Face fixed and plugged to joists / plywood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen considering a new Oak floor or Walnut flooring, always be aware that the complex task of installing a wood floor whether solid wood or engineered wood flooring is best left to an expert wood floor installer. A trained and experienced woo